<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَسْقُطُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَدُ الأَبَوَيْنِ:</span> بِابْنٍ، وَإِنْ نَزَلَ، وَأَبٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَوَلَدُ الأَبِ:</span> بِهَؤُلَاءِ الثلاثةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>، وَأَخٍ لِأَبَوَيْنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَابْنُ أَخٍ:</span> بِهَؤُلَاءِ، وَجَدٍّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَوَلَدُ الأُمِّ:</span> بِوَلَدٍ، وَوَلَدِ ابْنٍ وَإِنْ نَزَلَ، وَأَبٍ، وَأَبِيهِ وَإِنْ عَلَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ لَا يَرِثُ لِمَانِعٍ فِيهِ:</span> لَا يَحْجُبُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالعَصَبَةُ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> يَأْخُذُ مَا أَبْقَتِ الفُرُوضُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَإِنْ لَمْ يَبْقَ شَيْءٌ: سَقَطَ مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَإِنِ انْفَرَدَ أَخَذَ جَمِيعَ المَالِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> لَكِنْ لِلْجَدِّ وَالأَبِ ثَلَاثُ حَالَاتٍ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> فَيَرِثَانِ بِالتَّعْصِيبِ فَقَطْ: مَعَ عَدَمِ الوَلَدِ وَوَلَدِ الابْنِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَبِالفَرْضِ فَقَطْ: مَعَ ذُكُورِيَّتِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (الثلاثة) سقطت من (أ) و (ب) و (ج).</p> </div>